PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FA "road system" made up of 100
OL,8,Fhectares of wildflower meadows has
OL,9,Fbeen created in the South Downs
OL,10,FNational Park to help boost bee
OL,11,Fpopulations.
OL,13,FThe land, the size of 4,000 tennis
OL,14,Fcourts, has been set aside to create
OL,15,Fthe "bee lines" in farms, road verges,
OL,16,Fschool fields, cemeteries and football
OL,17,Fand golf clubs to help provide new
OL,18,Fhabitat to support struggling bee
OL,19,Fpopulations in Hampshire and Sussex.
OL,26,@oD@COUoD@OO]wD@EOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
