OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FA spokesman for the national park,
OL,8,Fwhich is marking World Bee Day on May
OL,9,F20, said there are 270 species of wild
OL,10,Fbees in the UK but 13 species have
OL,11,Fbeen lost with another 35 at risk of
OL,12,Fextinction.
OL,14,FHe said: "The 'bee lines' effectively
OL,15,Fcreate a 'road system' for pollinating
OL,16,Finsects, allowing them to move through
OL,17,Fthe landscape more easily.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,F"To date, the South Downs Trust, the
OL,8,Fofficial charity for the National
OL,9,FPark, has funded 37 projects and 106
OL,10,Fhectares of habitat has been
OL,11,Ftransformed into wildflower oases.
OL,13,F"A further eight projects, yet to be
OL,14,Fconfirmed, across Hampshire and Sussex
OL,15,Fwill benefit from more funding later
OL,16,Fthis year."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FJan Knowlson, biodiversity officer for
OL,8,Fthe national park, said: "It's
OL,9,Ffantastic to see this network of
OL,10,Fwildflower corridors really becoming
OL,11,Festablished and there are early signs
OL,12,Fthat bees and butterflies are
OL,13,Freturning, but there's still so much
OL,14,Fmore that needs to be done to help
OL,15,Fpollinators.
OL,26,@pD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,F"These insects have been on a steep
OL,8,Fdecline across the UK for several
OL,9,Fdecades and are now under threat from
OL,10,Fclimate change and habitat loss, so
OL,11,Fit's really important we create more
OL,12,Fspaces for pollinators to thrive.
OL,14,F"One out of every three mouthfuls of
OL,15,Four food depends on pollinators such
OL,16,Fas bees."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FShe added: "People can also do their
OL,8,Fbit to help on a smaller scale by
OL,9,Fsimply creating wilder areas of their
OL,10,Fgardens and planting some wildflower
OL,11,Fseeds.
OL,13,F"Working together we can turn this
OL,14,Faround and our countryside and towns
OL,15,Fcan once again be buzzing with bees."
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
