OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FSarah Womersley, a volunteer who helps
OL,8,Fmaintain a site at Blacknest Fields,
OL,9,Fin Binsted, Hampshire, said: "We're
OL,10,Fseeing a much more diverse range of
OL,11,Fflora in the meadows and that in turn
OL,12,Fis helping our pollinators.
OL,14,F"We've seen over 30 species of
OL,15,Fbutterflies on the field, more than 30
OL,16,Fspecies of bees and wasps and over 190
OL,17,Fdifferent species of moths.
OL,19,F"Seeing what Blacknest Fields has
OL,20,Fbecome over the past five years has
OL,21,Fbeen wonderful."
OL,26,@qD@^OUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
