OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778778356
OL,3,C'Road system' for bees 'boosting
OL,4,Cpopulations' across South Downs
OL,5,CNational Park
OL,7,FIan Forrest, a landowner who received
OL,8,Fa grant from the scheme for a 1.5-
OL,9,Fhectare field called Tangletrees, near
OL,10,FGraffham, West Sussex, said: "It's
OL,11,Fencouraging to see oxeye daisies and
OL,12,Fother species starting to thrive in
OL,13,Fthe new meadow.
OL,15,F"Creating habitat takes time, but this
OL,16,Fgrant has given us the chance to make
OL,17,Fa real start for pollinators and
OL,18,Fbiodiversity."
OL,26,@rD@^OUwD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
